{"tid":625780,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大愈要同身邊嘅人計得清清楚楚","createTime":"2018-04-11T17:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T08:10:00.000Z","uid":179186,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cffb41f31758776d99940e7aaf62576b732f9440","tid":625780,"uid":179186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:20:17.000Z","msg":"細個唔識野覺得你對人好<br />\n人地都會對你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我細個就對朋友幫得就幫<br />\n可能因為咁我對人地嘅要求好多時都會「是旦啦,冇所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」咁<br />\n但到依家投身社會之後<br />\n就發覺做人唔可以咁大方<br />\n有啲人就係睇中左你乜都冇所謂就單方面利用你<br />\n或者可能幫返你好少嘅野黎換取你更多嘅幫助<br />\n到依家終於明白咩叫對別人仁慈即係對自己殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以同咩人做乜野都好(除左自己屋企人/好熟嘅朋友)都係計下自己嘅得失先好去幫<br />\n唔係嘅話,蝕底嘅只有自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有啲1999,純粹發洩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2602b2936945a72f8eda7d417284366351343a8a","tid":625780,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:32:25.000Z","msg":"付出唔一定有回報"},{"pid":"19c15d7eedad7131648df1fbaf7a8fb167f24449","tid":625780,"uid":181666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"人係自私 所以真係唔可以太善良"},{"pid":"635750894ccc75d8f797d89186c622ee8b2860a5","tid":625780,"uid":179186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2602b2936945a72f8eda7d417284366351343a8a","tid":625780,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:32:25.000Z","msg":"付出唔一定有回報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"我明,所以幫人都係要睇人黎幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地對我好我先對返人好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656a44358760717b507abdd4ebd6a542e84e2199","tid":625780,"uid":179186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19c15d7eedad7131648